+# Fineract 还款计划生成深度分析报告
+
+## 1. 流程与入口
+
+### 1.1 核心调用链
+
+从 REST API 请求到生成还款计划的完整调用链如下：
+
+```mermaid
+flowchart TD
+    A["POST /api/v1/loans/{loanId}/schedule?command=calculateLoanSchedule"] --> B["LoanScheduleApiResource.calculateLoanScheduleOrSubmitVariableSchedule()"]
+    B --> C["LoanScheduleCalculationPlatformService.generateLoanScheduleForVariableInstallmentRequest()"]
+    C --> D["LoanScheduleCalculationPlatformService.calculateLoanSchedule()"]
+    D --> E["LoanMapper.generateSchedule()"]
+    E --> F["LoanScheduleGeneratorFactory.create(scheduleType, interestMethod)"]
+    F --> G["CumulativeDecliningBalanceInterestLoanScheduleGenerator.generate()"]
+    G --> H["AbstractCumulativeLoanScheduleGenerator.generate()"]
+    H --> I["DefaultScheduledDateGenerator.generateRepaymentPeriods()"]
+    H --> J["LoanApplicationTerms.calculateTotalInterestForPeriod()"]
+    H --> K["DefaultScheduledDateGenerator.adjustRepaymentDate()"]
+
+    style A fill:#e3f2fd,color:#0d47a1
+    style B fill:#bbdefb,color:#0d47a1
+    style C fill:#c8e6c9,color:#1a5e20
+    style G fill:#fff3e0,color:#e65100
+    style H fill:#fff3e0,color:#e65100
+    style J fill:#f3e5f5,color:#7b1fa2
+```
+
+### 1.2 关键类/方法职责
+
+| 序号 | 类名 | 方法名 | 职责说明 |
+|------|------|--------|----------|
+| 1 | [LoanScheduleApiResource](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/api/LoanScheduleApiResource.java#L52-L102) | `calculateLoanScheduleOrSubmitVariableSchedule()` | REST API 入口，处理 `/v1/loans/{loanId}/schedule` 的 POST 请求。根据 `command` 参数区分三种操作：`calculateLoanSchedule`（计算还款计划预览）、`addVariations`（添加还款计划变更）、`deleteVariations`（删除变更） |
+| 2 | [LoanScheduleCalculationPlatformService](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/service/LoanScheduleCalculationPlatformService.java#L23-L33) | `generateLoanScheduleForVariableInstallmentRequest()` / `calculateLoanSchedule()` | 平台级服务层，负责将 JSON 请求解析为内部数据结构，协调还款计划生成的全流程，包括参数校验、上下文构建和结果序列化 |
+| 3 | [LoanMapper](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/mapper/LoanMapper.java#L69-L75) | `generateSchedule()` | 根据贷款产品类型（`LoanScheduleType`）和利息计算方法（`InterestMethod`）从工厂中选择合适的 `LoanScheduleGenerator` 实例，并传入贷款条款、费用集合和节假日信息进行生成 |
+| 4 | [CumulativeDecliningBalanceInterestLoanScheduleGenerator](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/CumulativeDecliningBalanceInterestLoanScheduleGenerator.java#L28-L195) | `calculatePrincipalInterestComponentsForPeriod()` | 递减余额法（Declining Balance）的核心计算器。在每个还款周期内，按本金余额计算利息，再根据摊销方式（等额本息/等额本金）拆分本金和利息部分。支持利率变动、利息资本化、宽限期等复杂场景 |
+| 5 | [AbstractCumulativeLoanScheduleGenerator](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/AbstractCumulativeLoanScheduleGenerator.java#L71-L508) | `generate()` | 还款计划生成的主框架方法。负责：初始化计划参数、生成还款日期列表、逐周期计算本金/利息/费用、处理多笔放款（multi-disburse）、处理利息重算（interest recalculation）、合并费用与罚金、生成最终的 `LoanScheduleModel` |
+| 6 | [DefaultScheduledDateGenerator](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/DefaultScheduledDateGenerator.java#L46-L485) | `generateRepaymentPeriods()` / `adjustRepaymentDate()` | 还款日期生成器。根据还款频率（日/周/月/年）和间隔生成每期还款日期，并在生成后调用 `adjustRepaymentDate()` 进行工作日和节假日调整 |
+| 7 | [LoanApplicationTerms](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1044-L1092) | `calculateTotalInterestForPeriod()` | 贷款条款模型中的利息计算核心方法。根据利息计算方法（FLAT / DECLINING_BALANCE）、摊销方式（EQUAL_INSTALLMENTS / EQUAL_PRINCIPAL）、宽限期设置等，计算单个周期的利息金额 |
