+## 2. 算法实现
+
+### 2.1 等额本息（Declining Balance – Equal Installments）
+
+**计算公式：**
+
+等额本息方式下，每期还款总额（PMT）固定，计算公式为 Excel PMT 函数的实现：
+
+```
+PMT = P × r × (1 + r)^n / ((1 + r)^n - 1)
+
+其中：
+  P = 剩余本金余额（outstanding balance）
+  r = 周期利率（periodic interest rate）
+  n = 剩余还款期数（periods remaining）
+```
+
+每期拆分：
+```
+利息部分 = 剩余本金 × 周期利率
+本金部分 = PMT - 利息部分
+```
+
+**代码位置：**
+
+- PMT 计算：[LoanApplicationTerms.paymentPerPeriod()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1604-L1623)
+  ```java
+  double installmentAmount = FinanicalFunctions.pmt(
+      periodicInterestRate.doubleValue(), 
+      periodsRemaining.doubleValue(),
+      principalDouble, 
+      futureValue, 
+      false
+  );
+  ```
+- 本金计算：[LoanApplicationTerms.calculateTotalPrincipalForPeriod()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L974-L1002)
+- 利息计算：[LoanApplicationTerms.calculateDecliningInterestDueForInstallmentBeforeApplyingGrace()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1625-L1635)
+
+### 2.2 等额本金（Declining Balance – Equal Principal）
+
+**计算公式：**
+
+等额本金方式下，每期偿还的本金固定，利息随剩余本金递减：
+
+```
+每期固定本金 = 贷款总本金 / 剩余还款期数
+每期利息 = 剩余本金 × 周期利率
+每期还款总额 = 固定本金 + 当期利息
+```
+
+**代码位置：**
+
+- 固定本金计算：[LoanApplicationTerms.calculateEqualPrincipalDueForInstallment()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1678-L1695)
+  ```java
+  final Integer numberOfPrincipalPaymentPeriods = 
+      calculateNumberOfRemainingPrincipalPaymentPeriods(
+          this.actualNumberOfRepayments, periodNumber);
+  principal = this.principal.dividedBy(numberOfPrincipalPaymentPeriods, mc);
+  this.fixedPrincipalAmount = principal.getAmount();
+  ```
+
+### 2.3 利息计算基准（Day Count Convention）
+
+Fineract 支持多种天数计算基准，通过 `DaysInYearType` 和 `DaysInMonthType` 两个枚举类配置：
+
+#### DaysInYearType（年天数类型）
+
+| 枚举值 | 值 | 说明 | 代码位置 |
+|--------|-----|------|----------|
+| `ACTUAL` | 1 | 实际天数（闰年366天，平年365天） | [DaysInYearType.java](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInYearType.java#L35-L40) |
+| `DAYS_360` | 360 | 每年固定360天 | [DaysInYearType.java](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInYearType.java#L35-L40) |
+| `DAYS_364` | 364 | 每年固定364天 | [DaysInYearType.java](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInYearType.java#L35-L40) |
+| `DAYS_365` | 365 | 每年固定365天 | [DaysInYearType.java](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInYearType.java#L35-L40) |
+
+#### DaysInMonthType（月天数类型）
+
+| 枚举值 | 值 | 说明 | 代码位置 |
+|--------|-----|------|----------|
+| `ACTUAL` | 1 | 实际天数（28/29/30/31天） | [DaysInMonthType.java](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInMonthType.java#L33-L36) |
+| `DAYS_30` | 30 | 每月固定30天（30/360 惯例） | [DaysInMonthType.java](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInMonthType.java#L33-L36) |
+
+#### 周期利率计算
+
+周期利率的计算逻辑在 [LoanApplicationTerms.periodicInterestRate()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1399-L1468) 中实现：
+
+```java
+// 日利率 = 年名义利率 / 一年期数 / 100
+BigDecimal oneDayOfYearInterestRate = 
+    this.annualNominalInterestRate
+        .divide(loanTermPeriodsInYearBigDecimal, mc)
+        .divide(divisor, mc);
+
+// 周期利率 = 日利率 × 周期内天数
+periodicInterestRate = oneDayOfYearInterestRate.multiply(numberOfDaysInPeriod, mc);
+```
+
+其中 `numberOfDaysInPeriod` 的计算取决于 `DaysInMonthType`：
+- 如果是 `DAYS_30`，则每月按 30 天计算
+- 如果是 `ACTUAL`，则使用实际天数差
+
+一年期数由 [DefaultPaymentPeriodsInOneYearCalculator](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/DefaultPaymentPeriodsInOneYearCalculator.java#L30-L59) 计算：
+- 日频率 → 365
+- 周频率 → 52
+- 月频率 → 12
+- 年频率 → 1
+
+#### 配置类位置
+
+| 配置项 | 类名 | 路径 |
+|--------|------|------|
+| 年天数类型枚举 | [DaysInYearType](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInYearType.java) | `fineract-core/.../common/domain/DaysInYearType.java` |
+| 月天数类型枚举 | [DaysInMonthType](file:///app/fineract-core/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/common/domain/DaysInMonthType.java) | `fineract-core/.../common/domain/DaysInMonthType.java` |
+| 周期计算器 | [DefaultPaymentPeriodsInOneYearCalculator](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/DefaultPaymentPeriodsInOneYearCalculator.java) | `fineract-loan/.../domain/DefaultPaymentPeriodsInOneYearCalculator.java` |
+| 利息计算核心 | [LoanApplicationTerms.periodicInterestRate()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java#L1399-L1468) | `fineract-loan/.../domain/LoanApplicationTerms.java` |
