+
+### 问题 2：递归调整还款日可能导致栈溢出
+
+**问题描述：**
+
+[DefaultScheduledDateGenerator.recursivelyCheckNonWorkingDaysAndHolidaysAndWorkingDaysExemptionToGenerateNextRepaymentPeriodDate()](file:///app/fineract-loan/src/main/java/org/apache/fineract/portfolio/loanaccount/loanschedule/domain/DefaultScheduledDateGenerator.java#L211-L249) 使用递归方式处理非工作日和节假日调整。如果连续的非工作日/节假日数量过多（如极端情况下连续数月的节假日配置），递归深度可能超过 JVM 栈限制。
+
+**代码位置：**
+
+```java
+private AdjustedDateDetailsDTO recursivelyCheckNonWorkingDaysAndHolidaysAndWorkingDaysExemptionToGenerateNextRepaymentPeriodDate(
+        final AdjustedDateDetailsDTO adjustedDateDetailsDTO, ...) {
+    // ...
+    if ((holidayDetailDTO.isHolidayEnabled() && HolidayUtil.getApplicableHoliday(...) != null)
+            || WorkingDaysUtil.isNonWorkingDay(...)) {
+        // 递归调用自身
+        recursivelyCheckNonWorkingDaysAndHolidaysAndWorkingDaysExemptionToGenerateNextRepaymentPeriodDate(...);
+    }
+    return adjustedDateDetailsDTO;
+}
+```
+
+**影响场景：**
+- 配置了大量连续节假日（如某些国家有长达数周的公共假期）
+- 每周工作日配置极少（如仅配置 1-2 个工作日），导致需要递归多次才能找到下一个工作日
+- 在批量生成大量贷款还款计划时，每次生成都会触发递归，增加栈溢出风险
+
+**改进建议：**
+
+将递归改为迭代（while 循环）：
+
+```java
+// 伪代码：迭代版本
+private AdjustedDateDetailsDTO adjustRepaymentDateIterative(
+        AdjustedDateDetailsDTO adjustedDateDetailsDTO,
+        LoanApplicationTerms loanApplicationTerms,
+        HolidayDetailDTO holidayDetailDTO) {
+    
+    int maxIterations = 365; // 安全上限：最多调整一年
+    int iteration = 0;
+    
+    while (iteration < maxIterations) {
+        boolean needsAdjustment = false;
+        
+        // 检查非工作日
+        if (WorkingDaysUtil.isNonWorkingDay(holidayDetailDTO.getWorkingDays(), 
+                adjustedDateDetailsDTO.getChangedScheduleDate())) {
+            WorkingDaysUtil.updateWorkingDayIfRepaymentDateIsNonWorkingDay(...);
+            needsAdjustment = true;
+        }
+        
+        // 检查节假日
+        Holiday holiday = HolidayUtil.getApplicableHoliday(...);
+        if (holiday != null) {
+            HolidayUtil.updateRepaymentRescheduleDateToWorkingDayIfItIsHoliday(...);
+            needsAdjustment = true;
+        }
+        
+        if (!needsAdjustment) {
+            break;
+        }
+        iteration++;
+    }
+    
+    if (iteration >= maxIterations) {
+        throw new ScheduleDateException("Unable to find a valid repayment date within " + maxIterations + " days");
+    }
+    
+    return adjustedDateDetailsDTO;
+}
+```
+
